						<div class="postbody">I've got the IR controllers by Acclaim and I'm not a big fan.  I'd really like to see a RF version.  If I had the knowledge I'd do it myself, but I switched from EE to CS 6 years ago... crap it's been that long and I still don't have my degree <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" /></div>

